---

🎯 Must-Have Features (only as per problem)

Student Side

Register/Login.

Upload documents.

View submission status.

Get notifications (basic UI message).

SAG Bureau Side

See uploaded docs.

Mark as verified/rejected.

Finance Bureau Side

See verified docs.

Mark disbursed.

System

Authentication (basic email-password).

Secure file upload.

Status tracking from upload → verification → payment.

🛠️ Tech Stack (fastest to implement)

Frontend: React + Tailwind CSS (your strength).

Backend: Node.js + Express (only minimal APIs).

Database: MongoDB (for user, documents, status).

Storage: Local folder / MongoDB GridFS (skip AWS/GCP for hackathon).

---